item.title: Pause Fest 2016 Official Trailer
item.description:
Pause Fest 2016 Official Trailer

Discover how to make ideas happen, build successful products and master disruption at Pause 2016. Tickets Out Now - http://www.pause.melbourne Digital disruption has changed the way consumers behave and businesses operate. To truly understand what this means for you and your business, the conference program has been designed around the pillars of the startup - Creative, Tech, Business.
